00:31:32.670 --> 00:31:36.432
But if you were to defend the
hard pass, if you were to defend

00:31:36.432 --> 00:31:39.382
the mountains,
then if he chooses the easy

00:31:39.382 --> 00:31:44.180
pass, he gets both battalions in
