00:32:06.955 --> 00:32:11.054
some jargon -- it is the case
that the easy pass for the

00:32:11.054 --> 00:32:15.599
attacker, weakly dominates the
hard pass for the attacker.

00:32:15.599 --> 00:32:17.099
What do I mean by weakly
dominate?

00:32:17.099 --> 00:32:21.877
It means by choosing the easy
pass, he does at least as well,

00:32:21.877 --> 00:32:25.939
and sometimes better,
than he would have done had he

00:32:25.939 --> 00:32:29.738
chosen the hard pass.
