I'll say it again,

00:33:57.332 --> 00:34:00.237
Player i's strategy
"s'_i" is weakly

00:34:00.237 --> 00:34:03.724
dominated by her strategy
"s_i" if she always

00:34:03.724 --> 00:34:07.145
does at least as well by
choosing "s_i" than

00:34:07.145 --> 00:34:10.826
choosing "s'_i"
regardless of what everyone else

00:34:10.826 --> 00:34:14.543
does,
and sometimes she does strictly

00:34:14.543 --> 00:34:17.158
better.
It seems a pretty powerful

00:34:17.158 --> 00:34:18.993
